    <note>Shen(2) Yi [25143] CBD, citing SS, has mingzi with radical 102, Wuxing zhi, 17.12a has it as 9, and Wuxing zhi, 17.17a has it as 167. The cross references in Wuxing zhi make it clear that all three were the same person. He probably changed his mingzi since there are 4 other Deqing Shen(2) jinshi between 1070 and 1079, who all share the # 9 radical as a generational indicator. I am assuming that they were brothers, but may have been cousins. CBD, 1, 683.</note>
